{"tid":857532,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"依家d 90後係咪姓賴？無左隻Mouse連小小野都做唔到？","createTime":"2018-10-11T07:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T09:29:40.000Z","uid":19334,"like":21,"dislike":76,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"3b892acb64c41b5db2d6eef0eb696a8e2827f195","tid":857532,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:10:00.000Z","msg":"話說小妹要幫一間Design firm請人，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n在場每個人都做足哂準備，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有哂Profile，Job reference......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我忽發奇想，叫佢地Design個Logo，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁先睇到佢地係咩新鮮籮白皮，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就借左部公司最傳統d notebook（行緊XP），<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n限佢地5分鐘內畫同埋Present，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知隻90後突然舉手問有無Mouse借，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就反問佢有無錢借，串到佢一棟都無，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n後尾佢交唔到作品，就賴無Mouse唔識用，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家d 90後真係乜都賴得，唔好好裝備自己。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b418c3e1a67ad738ed1b19ba9102992147a3844","tid":857532,"uid":81308,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:10:59.000Z","msg":"2018年 xp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b70165097e5f1090c0100171e7abf85c1c4c633","tid":857532,"uid":128219,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:11:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5327bc8fd95455572d61377583b5d71469fc23f","tid":857532,"uid":17382,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0